ls_001-30716a" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-05T04:09:19.619+09:00">losing a fine opportunity through failure to act</seg><seg corresp="#KR1j0090_tls_001-30715a" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-05T04:11:00.266+09:00">losing a definite chance through failure to act</seg><seg corresp="#KR1j0090_tls_001-30714a" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-05T04:12:14.85+09:00">by passive consumption the mountain will become empty&gt; all will in the end be use up</seg><seg corresp="#KR1j0090_tls_001-30713a" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-05T04:13:13.322+09:00">remain a bystander and fail to save a situation</seg><seg corresp="#KR1j0090_tls_001-30712a" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-05T04:14:56.237+09:00">remain passive and see who wins</seg><seg corresp="#KR1j0090_tls_001-30710a" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-05T04:17:26.083+09:00">achieve things without taking overt action and not make big words</seg><seg corresp="#KR1j0090_tls_001-30707a" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-05T04:18:51.957+09:00">be inseparable awake or asleep</seg><seg corresp="#KR1j0090_tls_001-30706a" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-05T04:19:25.177+09:00">be restless both when awake and in bed</seg><seg corresp="#KR1j0090_tls_001-30708a" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-05T04:20:06.085+09:00">feel restless both when awake and when in bed.</seg><seg corresp="#KR1j0090_tls_001-30721a" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-05T04:21:53.532+09:00">sit on an unpromising stool</seg><seg corresp="#KR1j0090_tls_001-30722a" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-05T04:22:28.822+09:00">have a limited perspective on things</seg><seg corresp="#KR1j0090_tls_001-30723a" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-05T04:23:50.541+09:00">have a limited perspective on things</seg><seg corresp="#KR1j0090_tls_001-30724a" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-05T04:24:03.062+09:00">avoid sitting under the drains</seg><seg corresp="#KR1j0090_tls_001-30725a" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-05T04:25:15.492+09:00">典故：not sit under the drain</seg><seg corresp="#KR1j0090_tls_001-30726a" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-05T04:29:37.972+09:00">refuse to join a conflict and remain an observer</seg><seg corresp="#KR1j0090_tls_001-30727a" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-05T04:30:20.091+09:00">discuss things as a non-participant</seg><seg corresp="#KR1j0090_tls_001-30728a" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-05T04:31:02.483+09:00">wait impatiently for the next day</seg><seg corresp="#KR1j0090_tls_001-30729a" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-05T04:31:35.92+09:00">remain inactive and wait for the worst</seg><seg corresp="#KR1j0090_tls_001-30730a" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-05T04:32:03.003+09:00">remain inactive and wait for one's violent death</seg><seg corresp="#KR1j0090_tls_001-30731a" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-05T04:33:01.249+09:00">hold one's position and limiting one's perspectives</seg><seg corresp="#KR1j0090_tls_001-30732a" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-05T04:34:08.254+09:00">distribute the illegal booty without participating in obtaining it</seg><seg corresp="#KR1j0090_tls_001-30739a" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-05T04:36:02.102+09:00">lead a simple life</seg></p></div></body></text></TEI>